        <Parent_String>decanter wagons [300265312], wine coasters [300217324], coasters (containers) [300196479], accessory containers for food service [300198761], containers for serving and consuming food [300198760], culinary containers [300197577], containers by function or context [300197200], containers (receptacles) [300197197], Containers (hierarchy name) [300045611], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
